<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 20:07:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人在恐怖袭击后开枪打死以色列男子，涉嫌鲁莽杀人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-arrested-for-shooting-israeli-man-during-jerusalem-terror-attack/0000018c-3485-dc03-a9ec-3cffbea00000</link><description>以色列军警逮捕了预备役士兵阿维亚德·弗里贾（Aviad Frija），他认为被枪杀的犹太男子是袭击耶路撒冷公交车站的巴勒斯坦恐怖分子之一。极右部长：“民族英雄”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 19:37:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-arrested-for-shooting-israeli-man-during-jerusalem-terror-attack/0000018c-3485-dc03-a9ec-3cffbea00000</guid></item><item><title>加沙南部的恐怖景象：每平方公里18,000人断水断电</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/south-gazas-horror-scenario-18-000-people-per-square-km-without-water-or-power/0000018c-353e-dc03-a9ec-3d7fd74f0000</link><description>任何支持对汗尤尼斯发动地面进攻的以色列人——包括政治家——都必须记住，战后最终数据将放在世界上每一位外交部长和媒体的办公桌上</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 18:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/south-gazas-horror-scenario-18-000-people-per-square-km-without-water-or-power/0000018c-353e-dc03-a9ec-3d7fd74f0000</guid></item><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦抗议者瞄准犹太名厨拥有的费城沙拉三明治店</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/pro-palestinian-protesters-target-philadelphia-falafel-shop-owned-by-jewish-celebrity-chef/0000018c-3607-d3ba-af9f-ff27c6ff0000</link><description>大费城犹太联合会的两名高管表示，“仅仅因为以色列和犹太人的所有权而针对企业是公然的反犹太主义”。白宫表示针对此类餐厅是“反犹太主义且完全没有道理的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 18:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/pro-palestinian-protesters-target-philadelphia-falafel-shop-owned-by-jewish-celebrity-chef/0000018c-3607-d3ba-af9f-ff27c6ff0000</guid></item><item><title>前拜登官员警告加沙迫在眉睫的人道主义灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-biden-official-warns-of-humanitarian-disaster-in-gaza/0000018c-35b2-d5f2-a5cc-77b6ec630000</link><description>难民国际主席杰里米·科宁迪克“非常担心”加沙正处于由战争本身以外的因素造成的第二波重大死亡浪潮的风口浪尖，他毫不羞于批评拜登政府的行为</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 18:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-biden-official-warns-of-humanitarian-disaster-in-gaza/0000018c-35b2-d5f2-a5cc-77b6ec630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼活动分子在保护以定居者为目标的西岸村庄时遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/left-wing-israeli-activists-attacked-while-protecting-settler-targeted-west-bank-village/0000018c-35c4-d5f2-a5cc-77d471c10000</link><description>其中一名活动人士头部受伤，脸部和肋骨都有瘀伤，另一名活动人士则被喷了胡椒喷雾。自加沙战争爆发以来，由于定居者的暴力和威胁，活动人士一直在村庄里睡觉</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:56:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/left-wing-israeli-activists-attacked-while-protecting-settler-targeted-west-bank-village/0000018c-35c4-d5f2-a5cc-77d471c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教授在不太可能的战争中以学术换取农业领域</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-professors-swap-academic-for-agricultural-fields-in-unlikely-war-effort/0000018c-353a-d5f2-a5cc-773ec4c90000</link><description>哈马斯在 10 月 7 日的大屠杀中杀害了至少 40 名来自泰国的移民工人，之后又有数千人逃离该国。响应求助号召，学者们正在离开象牙塔，踏入加沙边境社区的现实生活</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:47:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-professors-swap-academic-for-agricultural-fields-in-unlikely-war-effort/0000018c-353a-d5f2-a5cc-773ec4c90000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》等媒体如何在针对以色列和哈马斯的假新闻战争中被武器化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-media-outlets-like-haaretz-are-weaponized-in-the-fake-news-wars-over-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-3076-d15f-a7af-b27664390000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，互联网上充斥着各种影响力行动，这些行动放大了假新闻并劫持《国土报》等可靠的新闻来源，以给人一种否认暴行和阴谋论的真实感觉。这就是新闻业如何被虚假信息战所利用</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-media-outlets-like-haaretz-are-weaponized-in-the-fake-news-wars-over-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-3076-d15f-a7af-b27664390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列儿科医生表示，哈马斯扣押的儿童人质遭受“可怕的心理虐待”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-held-children-hostages-under-terrible-psychological-abuse-pediatrician-says/0000018c-3520-dc03-a9ec-3d7b543a0000</link><description>照顾从哈马斯囚禁中获释的以色列儿童的医生分享了有关情况的信息，他说：“这些是我从大屠杀幸存者祖父那里听到的故事。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 15:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-held-children-hostages-under-terrible-psychological-abuse-pediatrician-says/0000018c-3520-dc03-a9ec-3d7b543a0000</guid></item><item><title>考虑到他们的利益，一些中东大国并不急于送行哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/their-interests-in-mind-some-regional-powers-arent-rushing-to-see-off-hamas/0000018c-3434-d5f2-a5cc-7634c3d50000</link><description>尽管面临美国和以色列的压力，土耳其埃尔多安、埃及塞西和其他领导人仍然认为，即使在战后，该恐怖组织仍可能是巴勒斯坦领导层的一部分</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 15:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/their-interests-in-mind-some-regional-powers-arent-rushing-to-see-off-hamas/0000018c-3434-d5f2-a5cc-7634c3d50000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人什么时候开始在光明节点燃蜡烛？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-did-jews-start-lighting-candles-on-hanukkah/0000017f-db2c-d3ff-a7ff-fbacdaba0000</link><description>现代传统认为光明节蜡烛是随着节日而诞生的，但约瑟夫斯没有听说过它们：看来我们是从异教徒农神节借来的</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 14:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-did-jews-start-lighting-candles-on-hanukkah/0000017f-db2c-d3ff-a7ff-fbacdaba0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯犯下了有记录的暴行。但一些虚假故事却让否认者大吃一惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-committed-documented-atrocities-but-a-few-false-stories-feed-the-deniers/0000018c-34f3-da74-afce-b5fbe24f0000</link><description>哈马斯恐怖分子 10 月 7 日犯下反人类罪的大量证据不应被以色列搜救组织、军官甚至萨拉·内塔尼亚胡散布的未经证实的故事所污染。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 14:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-committed-documented-atrocities-but-a-few-false-stories-feed-the-deniers/0000018c-34f3-da74-afce-b5fbe24f0000</guid></item><item><title>法院审理阻止荷兰向以色列出口 F-35 零部件的诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/court-hears-suit-to-stop-netherlands-exporting-f-35-parts-to-israel/0000018c-34e9-d340-a3cc-f7ffe2cd0000</link><description>荷兰人权组织辩称，以色列在加沙袭击中使用了美国制造的飞机，造成平民死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 13:10:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/court-hears-suit-to-stop-netherlands-exporting-f-35-parts-to-israel/0000018c-34e9-d340-a3cc-f7ffe2cd0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙去世之前，他创作了这部史诗般的犹太卷轴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/before-dying-in-gaza-he-created-this-epic-jewish-scroll/0000018c-34a5-d0a6-a19f-bfa7bb900000</link><description>21 岁的埃坦·罗森茨威格 (Eitan Rosenzweig) 在加沙被杀。他的艺术作品在他身后流传至今：“这个人将会变得很特别，”已故吉瓦蒂士兵的策展人波拉特·所罗门 (Porat Salomon) 说道。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/before-dying-in-gaza-he-created-this-epic-jewish-scroll/0000018c-34a5-d0a6-a19f-bfa7bb900000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日大屠杀之前，哈马斯做空以色列股票是否赚了数百万美元？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/did-hamas-make-billions-betting-against-israeli-shares-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-348d-d5f2-a5cc-769d7bea0000</link><description>在哈马斯袭击前几天，特拉维夫和华尔街市场上针对以色列的豪赌赚了数十亿美元。似乎有人提前知道了这个计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/did-hamas-make-billions-betting-against-israeli-shares-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-348d-d5f2-a5cc-769d7bea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对英国和法国等一些欧洲国家发出旅行警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warning-for-some-european-countries-including-u-k-and-france/0000018c-349f-d5f2-a5cc-769f24b10000</link><description>国家安全委员会呼吁海外以色列公民“避免展示以色列和犹太人的标志并避免聚会”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:11:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warning-for-some-european-countries-including-u-k-and-france/0000018c-349f-d5f2-a5cc-769f24b10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙失职：联合国秘书长古特雷斯必须下台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dereliction-of-duty-on-gaza-un-secretary-general-guterres-must-go/0000018c-33f2-dc03-a9ec-3ffb78620000</link><description>安东尼奥·古特雷斯在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后发表的评论表明，他的态度充耳不闻，不仅因为这次袭击引发了地区性、甚至可能是全球性的安全危机，而且还因为他的消极态度。这是联合国在世界舞台上的责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dereliction-of-duty-on-gaza-un-secretary-general-guterres-must-go/0000018c-33f2-dc03-a9ec-3ffb78620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女演员盖尔·加朵呼吁对哈马斯性暴力保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-actress-gal-gadot-calls-out-silence-over-sexual-based-violence-by-hamas/0000018c-347f-d5f2-a5cc-767fe34b0000</link><description>这位《神奇女侠》明星写道：“世界辜负了 10 月 7 日的女性，这是一个需要果断回应的紧急情况。”她与其他以色列和犹太女性一起强调了国际社会在谴责哈马斯暴行方面的犹豫不决</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:36:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-actress-gal-gadot-calls-out-silence-over-sexual-based-violence-by-hamas/0000018c-347f-d5f2-a5cc-767fe34b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙朋友的个人恳求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/a-personal-plea-from-a-friend-in-gaza/0000018c-3480-dc03-a9ec-3cfbc1670000</link><description>“我们真正需要的是推土机来挖掘并将我们深深地埋入我们的土地”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/a-personal-plea-from-a-friend-in-gaza/0000018c-3480-dc03-a9ec-3cfbc1670000</guid></item><item><title>弗吉尼亚州光明节烛光仪式因以色列和加沙紧张局势而取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hanukkah-candle-lighting-ceremony-in-virginia-cancelled-over-israel-gaza-tensions/0000018c-33d9-dc03-a9ec-3ffba2f20000</link><description>据弗吉尼亚半岛犹太联合社区称，活动组织者只有在加沙停火的呼吁下才同意恢复仪式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 10:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hanukkah-candle-lighting-ceremony-in-virginia-cancelled-over-israel-gaza-tensions/0000018c-33d9-dc03-a9ec-3ffba2f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何确定远方哈马斯扣押的人质的死亡？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-did-israel-determine-hamas-killed-hostages-left-in-gaza/0000018c-342a-dc03-a9ec-3c7bbf050000</link><description>为确定人质命运而建立的复杂而雄心勃勃的项目：一个新委员会正在观察、分析和比较视频剪辑，并使用支持证据和情报信息，以得出关键结论</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 10:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-did-israel-determine-hamas-killed-hostages-left-in-gaza/0000018c-342a-dc03-a9ec-3c7bbf050000</guid></item></channel></rss>